ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百年有大把印度盧比<br />\n<br />\n好玩，火車都好企理<br />\n儘量飲樽裝水、可樂同食好西，就唔會有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTHX 先, <br />\n有乜好西推介先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗住去9日, 如果我用4000蚊HKD 對做盧比夠唔夠用?"},{"pid":"4ff121c9b24e0b48770bff378fc1251fb34a1ba7","tid":375682,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"巴打你一行幾多人？<br />\n路線方面你可以搭火車 / 搵人包車由德里去Agra （即係泰姬陵個城）留兩三日，再坐過夜火車去Varanasi，亦有廉航德里直飛Varanasi<br />\n<br />\n火車可以去呢度上網訂，不過好多年前既事，唔記得晒過程 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.irctc.co.in/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irctc.co.in%2F&d=Pa5JOx7vR4VOERarhS4dfE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=fe23911b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.irctc.co.in/</a><br />\n揀艙位至少要3AC，即係有冷氣同基本設施既臥鋪，一齊坐既都係白領、中產階級，易溝通好多，再高級就2AC同1AC<br />\n<br />\n一定要飲樽裝水，出街食飯亦最好飲熱飲 (Masala Chai <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"327ef16f7f1009781f17ba0a524a98c93ad8a38a","tid":375682,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"男仔就無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c134ab9f1439cd2fa6e32f82a34a6786190abec","tid":375682,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"近排中印火藥味咁濃<br />\n你仲敢去印度"}]}